data.description: Incredibly maintained and updated 2 story in highly desired Hunting Creek! With plenty of room for a growing family, This freshly painted brick, 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home has it all! Located just seconds from restaurants, nightlife, parks, River access, Huntingcreek Country Club, Harrods Creek Park with hiking trails and kayaking, and so much more, its no wonder why This neighborhood is so popular. As for the house, the upgrades, updates and modernization speak for themselves. A wonderful custom, stained wood double entry door opens up to fabulously modernized foyer and living room with tile and refinished hardwood floors respectively. You'll notice the modern lighting package that has been installed throughout including many that are French Gold. The kitchen has been completely remodeled with French Gold hardware, quartz countertops, Stainless steel appliances, a newly added Gas Range, soft close cabinet doors and drawers, and a pantry with roll out shelving. The first floor is rounded out with a family room with Fireplace and hardwood floors, beautiful full bath room with custom tile and an office that is perfect for that quite get away. Upstairs, features a large Primary Suite with full frameless custom tile shower, double bowl furniture vanity and opens into a large walk in closet. Three more large bedrooms and a huge laundry room that has a great space for a folding table to be added. The basement is large and wide open with two dedicated spaces that can be used for multiple uses. Game room, entertaining, media room, office or just a place to store the teenagers. The prior laundry room hook ups are still available in basement if someone wants two laundry rooms or wishes to make the 2nd floor laundry a small bedroom or nursery! All of this with some amazing updates and perks including: Wainscotting, new roof sept 2022, resurfaced driveway June 2023, covered and shingled rear patio 2023, whole house air purifier/dehumidifier connected to HVAC, beautiful and peaceful backyard, large corner lot, fresh painted brick and shutters for that incredible curb appeal Hurry to see this wonderful home!
